Gejengel is an audio player which focuses on performance and simplicity, yet with a nice set of features.

Required dependencies to build the source archive:
gtkmm
libsexymm
taglib
libnotify
sqlite
imagemagick (built with c++ support)

Optional dependencies:
lastfmlib (lastfm plugin)
dbus-glib (dbus plugin)
openal (openal output)
alsa-lib (alsa output)
pulseaudio (pulseaudio output)
gtest (build unittests)

Credits:
Last.fm logo: http://www.gorvan.com
